title: Morrissey : Complete Discography (Apple Lossless)
description:
Morrissey&#039;s complete discography, including some singles.

Greatest Hits (2008)
I Have Forgiven Jesus (Single)
Kill Uncle 
KROQ (Live)
Live At Earl&#039;s Court (Live)
Live at Hollywood Bowl (Live)

I think that&#039;s it.  Add to it if you would like, as long as it&#039;s lossless.
What would be great is the singles box sets and b-sides from the 80s and early 90s.   Thanks! Please do this if you own these sets.
